            "id": "4573201",
            "title": "Delta Air Lines Non-GAAP EPS of $0.64 beats by $0.07, revenue of $15.85B beats by $1.03B",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Delta Air Lines <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20465542-delta-air-lines-announces-march-quarter-2026-financial-results\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DAL\" title=\"Delta Air Lines, Inc.\">DAL</a></span>): Q1 Non-GAAP EPS of $0.64 <span> beats by $0.07</span>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $15.85B (+12.9% Y/Y) <span> beats by $1.03B</span>.</li>\n<li><p data-eci=\"true\">Guiding to low-teens revenue growth in the June quarter on flat capacity growth, reflecting strong demand momentum, meaningful capacity reductions, and rapid actions to recapture higher fuel\\</p></li>\n<li><p>Expect June quarter pre-tax profit of around $1 billion, on a more than $2 billion increasein fuel expense at the forward curve</p></li>\n<li>\n<p>Financial Guidance</p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\"><div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<span class=\"sa-table-scroll-wrapper sa-hide-scrollbar\"><span data-intersection-boundary=\"start\" data-test-id=\"table-scroll-wrapper-boundary-start\"></span><div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<span class=\"sa-table-scroll-wrapper sa-hide-scrollbar\"><span data-intersection-boundary=\"start\" data-test-id=\"table-scroll-wrapper-boundary-start\"></span><table data-should-enlarge=\"true\"><tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"> </td>\n<td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>2Q26</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Total Revenue YoY (%)</p></td>\n<td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Up low-teens vs 9.39% consensus</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Operating Margin</p></td>\n<td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>6% - 8%</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Earnings Per Share</p></td>\n<td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>$1.00 - $1.50 vs $1.59 consensus</p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<span data-intersection-boundary=\"end\" data-test-id=\"table-scroll-wrapper-boundary-end\"></span></span><button class=\"sa-table-enlarge-button\" type=\"button\">Click to enlarge</button>\n</div>\n<span data-intersection-boundary=\"end\" data-test-id=\"table-scroll-wrapper-boundary-end\"></span></span><button class=\"sa-table-enlarge-button\" type=\"button\">Click to enlarge</button>\n</div></div>\n</li>\n<li>Shares <span>+7.7%</span> PM.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
